===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|langouste|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|locusta||locust, crustacean, lobster|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈləʊ.kəst/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈloʊ.kəst/}}
* {{audio|en-us-locust.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A type of [[grasshopper]] in the family [[Acrididae]] that flies in [[swarm]]s and is very [[destructive]] to [[crop]]s and other [[vegetation]].
# A [[locust tree]].

